name: Yakuza Cats Society [Disposal, official link changed]

metadata.description: The Yakuza Cat Society, set in the back alley of yakuza society, is a unique collection of 8,930 yakuza cats.The 1st Oyabun of the Yakuza Cats Society had grown old and passed away at the age of 17. Later on, the right and the left hand, leading a cat-and-dog life, went their separate ways. They have the home of their respective organizations based in different regions: one in Tokyo, and the other in Osaka. They have been in a fierce fight ever since, aiming to rule all of Japan.Join the syndicate you want by staking yakuza cats, expand your syndicate in the region, and become Yakuza Oyabun that rules the whole of Japan!Starting with the Yakuza War, future areas and perks can be unlocked by the community through roadmap activation.
metadata.name: Yakuza Cats
